<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Marinate pork in shallow dish in fridge up to 4 hours]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[braise in oven, turning occasionally, 1.5 hr at 160C, covered]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[uncover, raise heat to 190C, another 20m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[skim fat and serve]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
optional: to make a thicker sauce, pour juices into hot wok, add half cornstarch mixture, bring to boil, cook 2m adding remaining half as required]]></step>
</directions>
